e between the two kingdoms and brought the war to an end.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705193,"age":45,"year":"1337","toYear":"1453","julianDay":2209390,"title":"The Hundred Years' War","description":"The Hundred Years' War between France and England was largely due to the question of legitimate succession to the French crown.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When Margery de l'Orti was born about 1292, in Axford, Wiltshire, England, her father, John de l’Orti, was 17 and her mother, Mrs. John de l'Orti, was 14. She had at least 3 sons with Henry de Sturmy. She died before 1341."},"et":{"about 1292–BEF 1341":"umbes 1292–enne 1341","1292–1341":"1292–1341","1290–1338":"1290–1338","1311–1382":"1311–1382","1322–Male":"1322–Surnud","1325–1381":"1325–1381","1277–1295":"1277–1295","1279–Female":"1279–Surnud","about 1292":"umbes 1292","1341":"1341","1295":"1295","1382":"1382","1381":"1381","1292":"1292","1290":"1290","1338":"1338","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","BEF 1295":"enne 1295","1325":"1325","BEF 1341":"enne 1341","1279":"1279","1311":"1311","1322":"1322","1453":"1453","1277":"1277","ABT 1322":"umbes 1322","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Of Burbach,Wiltshire,England":"Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Burbage, Wiltshire, England":"Burbage, Wiltshire, England","Axford, Wiltshire, England":"Axford, Wiltshire, England"},"fi":{"about 1292–BEF 1341":"noin 1292–ennen vuotta 1341","1292–1341":"1292–1341","1290–1338":"1290–1338","1311–1382":"1311–1382","1322–Male":"1322–Kuollut","1325–1381":"1325–1381","1277–1295":"1277–1295","1279–Female":"1279–Kuollut","about 1292":"noin 1292","1341":"1341","1295":"1295","1382":"1382","1381":"1381","1292":"1292","1290":"1290","1338":"1338","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","BEF 1295":"ennen vuotta 1295","1325":"1325","BEF 1341":"ennen vuotta 1341","1279":"1279","1311":"1311","1322":"1322","1453":"1453","1277":"1277","ABT 1322":"noin 1322","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Of Burbach,Wiltshire,England":"Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningasku